(What are these two people)

13
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:41,080
(doing?)

14
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:42,640
(And a woman is stalking them?)

15
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:46,360
(Isn't it too exciting
for someone my age?)

16
00:00:46,360 --> 00:00:48,400
(The candy couple really came true.)

17
00:00:48,480 --> 00:00:50,640
♪Hey, do not blink at me♪

18
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:52,470
Is she gone?

19
00:00:52,480 --> 00:00:56,104
♪About love all day♪

20
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,200
Not yet.

21
00:00:58,200 --> 00:01:01,039
♪Remember to reply to me♪

22
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,600
How long do I need to wait?

23
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,960
My neck is a little tired.

24
00:01:04,473 --> 00:01:05,400
♪For not knowing how you think♪

25
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:06,240
She's gone.

26
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:10,960
Then I'll get going.

27
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:39,600
Hello.

28
